<% provide(:title, "Home") %>
<div class="container-fluid block-1">
  <div class="layer">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 center-lg">
        <h1>SHE | The Web App</h1>
        <h2>Relationship Simplified</h2>
        <%= link_to 'Sign Up', signup_path, class: 'btn-lg' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid block-2">
  <div class="row row-block-2">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <%= image_tag("SheLogo1.png") %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h1>What is SHE?</h1>
      <p>
        SHE is a cross platform fake girlfriend web application. SHE was
        created so that you can convince your friends and family that you have
        a girlfriend. Need to impress your family? We got you covered. Need to
        impress your friends? We can do that. Need to impress your coworkers?
        We have the answer.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid block-3">
  <div class="row row-block-3">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <h1>How Does it Work?</h1>
      <p>
        She works with a number of different applications in order to
        convince other people that you have a girlfriend. SHE uses Twitter
        to direct message you. SHE can like your posts on Facebook. And SHE
        can send you text messages. All of these features can be used to prove
        to others that you have a girlfriend.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag("SheLogo1.png") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid block-4">
  <div class="row row-block-4">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
      <%= image_tag("FakeConvo.png") %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h1>How Do I Sign Up?</h1>
      <p>
        Go to the top of this page and click on the sign up link. Fill
        out the form. And then our application can send you text messages as
        well as interact with you on Twitter and Facebook. You'll be soon on
        your way to impressing others with your totally fake girlfriend.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
